label: A5B8_cI52_217_ce_cg-001
title: $\gamma$-Brass (Cu$_{5}$Zn$_{8}$, $D8_{2}$) Structure
comments:
$\gamma$-brass comes in a variety of compositions. See the \href{current_web_home_dir/A3B10_cI52_229_e_fh-001}{$D8_{1}$} and \href{current_web_home_dir/A4B9_cP52_215_ei_3efgi-001}{$D8_{3}$} structure pages for more information. 
 We use the data from (Gourdon, 2007) for Cu$_{5.00}$Zn$_{8.00}$. At this composition the authors state that the sites are fully occupied. 
 (Mizutani, 2010) classifies this as a ``I-cell'' $\gamma$-brass.
